348
00:47:28,559 --> 00:47:31,687
奈里,炸药包带着!
Nellie. Take the satchel charge.

349
00:47:32,462 --> 00:47:34,487
听到了没?快!
You hear me? Move!

350
00:47:41,071 --> 00:47:42,766
你会掩护我吧?
You're gonna cover me, right?

351
00:47:42,906 --> 00:47:44,931
我一起去,从左翼进攻
I'll go with you. We flank left.

352
00:47:45,709 --> 00:47:47,939
我掩护你们,烟幕弹
I'll cover you. Smoke and cover.

353
00:47:48,078 --> 00:47:50,012
我办得到
I can do this.

354
00:47:52,716 --> 00:47:54,650
我办得到
I can do this.

355
00:48:04,528 --> 00:48:06,428
投掷烟幕弹!
Smoke 'em up!

356
00:48:11,902 --> 00:48:13,836
掩护他!
Cover up.

357
00:49:05,222 --> 00:49:06,689
操!
Shit!

358
00:49:13,530 --> 00:49:16,556
操,日本队被达阵了!
Shit. Goddamn Nipponese touchdown!

359
00:49:17,501 --> 00:49:19,833
“塞班岛”

360
00:49:24,808 --> 00:49:26,639
0500时提高警觉
Heads up around 0500.

361
00:49:26,777 --> 00:49:30,269
补给品和弹药会送过去，完毕
You're going to have replacements
and ammo coming up. Over.

362
00:49:31,648 --> 00:49:33,707
收到，请确认新口令
Roger. Make sure
they have the new password.

363
00:49:33,850 --> 00:49:36,148
问“猎风”，答“战士”
Challenge: "Wind." Answer: "Talkers."

364
00:49:36,286 --> 00:49:38,117
一位纳瓦荷弟兄取的名字
That's what one of our Navajo brothers
calls us.

365
00:49:38,255 --> 00:49:39,620
觉得怎么样？完毕
 What do you think? Over.

366
00:49:40,724 --> 00:49:42,988
“猎风战士”我喜欢
"Windtalkers," I like it. 

367
00:49:43,126 --> 00:49:46,493
好拉，老友，一夜平安，完毕
OK, Kemo Sabe,
keep your butts down tonight. Over.

368
00:49:48,398 --> 00:49:50,923
这口粮真难吃
Biscuits? How can you ruin biscuits?

369
00:49:51,468 --> 00:49:54,835
你还真他妈爱抱怨
You are a whiny son of a bitch
right now, aren't you?

370
00:49:57,107 --> 00:50:01,237
塞班晚上10点,东岸几点?
2200 hours in jungle hell - what does
that make it on the East Coast?

371
00:50:01,611 --> 00:50:03,875
我怎么会知道
How the fucking hell should I know?

372
00:50:04,715 --> 00:50:06,649
7点…
Just seven...

373
00:50:07,984 --> 00:50:09,918
星期日早上8点
It's 8am, Sunday morning.

374
00:50:10,587 --> 00:50:13,420
希望我的床昨晚没被篡位
I hope my side of the bed
didn't get taken up Saturday night.

375
00:50:13,623 --> 00:50:17,616
这么不放心她,迟早胃溃疡
Nell, you'll give yourself an ulcer,
you keep worrying about her.

376
00:50:17,761 --> 00:50:19,854
这样我就可以回罗德岛了
Might get my ass
sent back to Rhody, though.

377
00:50:19,996 --> 00:50:24,296
罗德岛辣妹不少哦
There's plenty of dollies outside
of Rhode Island, Nell. Many plenty.

378
00:50:24,434 --> 00:50:27,597
-这里肯定没半个
-这还用说
- Well, there sure as shit ain't any here.
- Ain't that the truth.

379
00:50:27,738 --> 00:50:32,801
她们全挤在德通海滩
世界上最美的女人
That's cos they're all in Daytona Beach.
The most beautiful women in the world.

380
00:50:32,943 --> 00:50:35,673
战前有一次
This one time, before the war,

381
00:50:35,812 --> 00:50:42,718
我躺在沙滩上,有个美女…
叫茉莉,从水里上岸来
I'm lyin' on the beach and this sweet little
thing named Molly comes out the water.

382
00:50:43,387 --> 00:50:46,686
走到我身边,问我饿不饿
She walks straight up to me
and asks me if I'm hungry...

383
00:50:47,391 --> 00:50:49,723
因为她只吃条小热狗
cos she's havin' a weenie roast.

384
00:50:49,860 --> 00:50:51,691
哇靠!
Shit! Damn.

385
00:50:52,062 --> 00:50:54,223
于是我和茉莉…爽
Yeah, me and Molly, oh boy.

386
00:50:59,336 --> 00:51:02,635
现在却困在塞班岛上
身上背个巨无霸打火机
Now I'm on Saipan with this
giant Zippo strapped to my back

387
00:51:02,773 --> 00:51:04,968
专门烤人肉
and I'm roastin' human beings.

388
00:51:10,981 --> 00:51:14,917
为什么会自愿从军
我实在搞不懂
Why I volunteered... beyond me.

389
00:51:17,053 --> 00:51:19,521
我倒是觉得蛮骄傲的
Damn, I'm proud to be here.

390
00:51:19,656 --> 00:51:22,022
我全家都是海军陆战队
My whole family's been in the Corps.

391
00:51:22,959 --> 00:51:24,950
老爸是终身职
My old man, he's a lifer.

392
00:51:25,328 --> 00:51:27,922
海上陆上都不可一世
An ass-kicker on the land and on the sea.

393
00:51:28,532 --> 00:51:30,432
在家一样作威作福
Around the house too.

394
00:51:35,038 --> 00:51:37,233
现在可能收敛点了
Maybe now he'll back off.

395
00:51:44,681 --> 00:51:46,615
帕帕斯
Pappas, I...

396
00:51:48,218 --> 00:51:50,277
希望你能帮个忙
I want you to do me a favor.

397
00:51:52,656 --> 00:51:54,817
万一我出了事
If anything should happen to me,

398
00:51:54,958 --> 00:51:57,688
这个请交给我太太
you make sure that my wife gets this.

399
00:52:00,330 --> 00:52:02,798
这是她亲手挑的
I mean, she picked them out and all.

400
00:52:03,266 --> 00:52:05,234
不要说这种话,奈尔
Don't talk like that, Nell.

401
00:52:06,603 --> 00:52:09,163
连玩笑都不要开
You don't even joke about shit like that.

402
00:52:09,840 --> 00:52:13,105
戴回去,你会平安回家
Now you put that ring back on.
You're goin' home.

403
00:53:10,233 --> 00:53:12,463
喝过才谢我还不迟
Don't thank me till you've tried it.

404
00:53:13,003 --> 00:53:15,198
发信时你不在
You missed mailcall.

405
00:53:15,338 --> 00:53:18,398
“乔伊恩得斯收
丽塔史维登寄”

406
00:53:25,549 --> 00:53:27,642
他们在干嘛?
What the hell are they doin'?

407
00:53:28,518 --> 00:53:31,248
不知道,日落后就忙个不停
I don't know.
They've been doin' it since sundown.

408
00:53:37,961 --> 00:53:40,191
听起来像是祈祷
Sounds like some kind of prayer.

409
00:53:47,637 --> 00:53:49,798
或许他们知道我们的命令
Maybe they know our orders.

410
00:54:04,621 --> 00:54:06,486
你下得了手吗,乔伊?
Think you could do it, Joe?

411
00:54:06,623 --> 00:54:08,648
不要一直想这问题,韩德森
Give it a rest, Henderson.

412
00:54:09,993 --> 00:54:12,484
不要想?我试过,可是…
Give it a rest? I keep tryin', but...

413
00:54:14,030 --> 00:54:16,055
该杀的是日本人,不是自己人
I'm here to kill Japs, not marines.

414
00:54:21,738 --> 00:54:24,172
你是个勇士，亚吉
I saw you a warrior, Yahzee...

415
00:54:25,208 --> 00:54:27,699
你是家族的荣耀
You will make your family proud.

416
00:55:17,127 --> 00:55:19,755
你在干嘛,老弟?
What the hell you think you're doin', boy?

417
00:55:19,863 --> 00:55:22,093
正要穿上制服
Getting on my uniform.

418
00:55:22,265 --> 00:55:25,860
知道你跟日本人
有什么差别吗?
You know the difference
between you and a Jap, Yahzee?

419
00:55:28,705 --> 00:55:30,605
差在制服
It's that uniform.

420
00:55:31,274 --> 00:55:33,208
仅此而已
That's it.

421
00:55:34,811 --> 00:55:36,608
我了解你们这些人
See, I know you people.

422
00:55:37,080 --> 00:55:40,641
我清楚你们这些凤眼野蛮人
I know what kind
of slanty-eyed savage you are, boy.

423
00:55:41,051 --> 00:55:43,713
落单时当心一点
You ought to be careful out here all alone.

424
00:55:44,521 --> 00:55:46,455
没有人照顾你时
No baby-sitter.

425
00:55:47,023 --> 00:55:48,957
我可能会把你看成日本鬼子
I might just take you for a Jap.

426
00:55:50,126 --> 00:55:52,390
你要让我穿衣服吗,奇克?
You gonna let me get dressed, Chick?

427
00:55:52,495 --> 00:55:55,623
还是继续演无知的白痴?
Or keep demonstrating
what an ignorant fool you are?

428
00:56:00,704 --> 00:56:03,002
无知的白痴是吧?
How's that for an ignorant fool?

429
00:56:20,857 --> 00:56:22,848
拿啊,你试试看
Go ahead, try again.

430
00:56:34,504 --> 00:56:36,597
你不是想干什么吗?
You gonna do somethin'?

431
00:56:58,328 --> 00:56:59,795
奇克,住手
Chick! Come on!

432
00:56:59,896 --> 00:57:01,830
走开!
Get off me!

433
00:57:21,451 --> 00:57:23,976
-你没事吧,班?
-没事
- You OK, Ben?
- Yeah.

434
00:57:24,120 --> 00:57:26,384
班?恶心
Ben? Shit.

435
00:57:28,925 --> 00:57:33,624
我以为他是日本人
杀我弟兄,偷穿制服
I thought he was a Jap. You know,
killed some marine for that uniform.

436
00:57:35,398 --> 00:57:37,263
再扯嘛,奇克
Sure you did, Chick.

437
00:57:37,700 --> 00:57:40,464
死红番不像日本鬼子吗?
Damn Injun looks just like
a Jap, don't he?

438
00:57:40,603 --> 00:57:42,503
我不是死红番
Look, I'm no damn Injun.

439
00:57:43,239 --> 00:57:48,108
我是纳瓦荷人
母系是苦水族,父系是塔楼族
I'm Navajo, of the Bitter Water People,
born for the Towering House clan.

440
00:57:51,848 --> 00:57:53,873
但长相蛮像日本人
But you do look like a Nip.

441
00:57:54,017 --> 00:57:58,920
下次要洗澡先通知我
否则我踢你屁股
Next time you decide to take a bath,
Private, let me know, or I'll kick your ass.

442
00:58:02,859 --> 00:58:04,793
妈的败类
Fuckin' shitbird.

443
00:58:05,962 --> 00:58:08,590
他随时都需要人照顾
Supposed to be with a baby-sitter
all the time, I thought.

444
00:58:08,765 --> 00:58:10,596
连出去打鱼时也一样
Out here huntin' salmon and shit.

445
00:58:12,936 --> 00:58:17,396
昨晚你看到的是
我们的庇护仪式
That ceremony you saw last night?
It's called a protection ceremony.

446
00:58:18,374 --> 00:58:24,335
纳瓦荷人相信尸体未安葬前
灵魂会一直待在附近
Navajo believe, untila body's given
a proper burial, the spirits stay near it.

447
00:58:24,848 --> 00:58:29,285
我们称恶灵为仙邸司
Chindis - that's what
we call evilspirits. Demons.

448
00:58:32,055 --> 00:58:35,024
我从小不曾认真想过这问题
I haven't thought much about it
since I was a kid.

449
00:58:35,158 --> 00:58:37,524
直到我目睹这些死尸
Till I saw those dead bodies.

450
00:58:37,660 --> 00:58:40,151
你是说你看得到鬼魂?
You telling me you saw ghosts, Private?

451
00:58:40,263 --> 00:58:42,629
不,我是说我不再害怕了
No, Sergeant. I'm telling you
I won't freeze up again.

452
00:58:43,132 --> 00:58:46,101
因为你朋友在你额头上抹灰?
Because your buddy
smeared ash on your forehead?

453
00:58:46,236 --> 00:58:50,468
没错,因为我朋友
在我额头上抹灰
That's right. Cos my buddy
smeared ash on my forehead.

454
00:58:58,248 --> 00:59:00,307
你看过鬼吗?
You ever see ghosts?

455
00:59:05,221 --> 00:59:08,987
不要再问傻问题了
这是命令
No more stupid questions today, Private.
That's an order.

456
00:59:40,657 --> 00:59:42,591
真好听
Sounds beautiful.

457
00:59:43,326 --> 00:59:45,294
无师自通吗?
You, uh, you self-taught?

458
00:59:46,129 --> 00:59:48,222
我爸爸常吹
My dad was always playing.

459
00:59:49,232 --> 00:59:52,360
他们不是说“拼不过他就…”
You know what they say:
if you can't beat 'em...

460
00:59:52,502 --> 00:59:57,701
正确,这是我爸送我的
No shit. My dad, he...
he gave me this thing.

461
00:59:59,008 --> 01:00:01,533
他以前叫我小猪魔笛
Used to call me the Pied Piper of the Pigs.

462
01:00:01,678 --> 01:00:05,512
我一吹它们就过来吃饲料
Used to bring 'em in for feeding
with this little tune I played.

463
01:00:06,616 --> 01:00:09,710
我知道你不会停止吹笛子
I know I ain't gonna get you
to quit playin' that thing, so...

464
01:00:09,852 --> 01:00:12,412
所以“拼不过他就…”
like you just said, if you can't beat 'em...

465
01:00:12,555 --> 01:00:14,785
我觉得声音不协调
I don't think it's gonna work.

466
01:00:16,292 --> 01:00:19,455
反正别无他法,管他的
Well, we ain't got much else
to do out here. What the hell?

467
01:00:20,663 --> 01:00:22,290
好吧
OK.

468
01:00:23,066 --> 01:00:25,830
你起音,我来和
All right, you lead off. I'll follow you.

469
01:01:03,840 --> 01:01:05,899
第二侦查队0600出发
2nd Recon Company will move out
at 0600 

470
01:01:06,042 --> 01:01:07,566
沿四号路搜索下去
and scout along road 04.

471
01:01:07,710 --> 01:01:11,271
椰林西北边可能遭到轻微抵抗
You can expect light resistance
northwest of the palm grove. Over.

472
01:01:12,281 --> 01:01:16,445
收到，何谓“轻微”？
没有任何抵抗是轻微的，完毕
Roger. What do you mean, light?
No resistance is light! Over.

473
01:01:17,487 --> 01:01:19,387
记住座右铭不问为什么
Remember, marine, "Ours is not to
question why, 

474
01:01:19,522 --> 01:01:20,614
只管拼命与牺牲
ours is but to do or die."

475
01:01:20,757 --> 01:01:22,349
“永远忠诚”完毕
Semper Fi. Over.

476
01:01:34,037 --> 01:01:37,006
亲爱的乔伊,你到底怎么了?
Dear Joe, how the hell are you?

477
01:01:38,041 --> 01:01:42,535
因为你不爱写信
就应该音讯全无吗?
Or, given that you're not much of a
writer, should I not expect an answer?

478
01:01:42,678 --> 01:01:45,545
报上说,我军战果辉煌
The newspapers say
our boys are doing great.

479
01:01:45,681 --> 01:01:50,118
但我想记者都没看到
肯尼欧湾医院的伤兵
But I don't think the reporters
have been to Kaneohe Bay Hospital.

480
01:01:51,220 --> 01:01:54,280
前几天在瓦基基捡到只流浪狗
I found a stray dog
the other day on Waikiki.

481
01:01:54,424 --> 01:01:57,086
带回家洗个澡留下来养
I gave him a bath and took him in.

482
01:01:57,226 --> 01:02:00,684
它令我想起你,但它比较可爱
He reminded me of you - but cuter.

483
01:02:02,598 --> 01:02:05,192
至少它晚上给我温暖
At least he keeps me warm at night.

484
01:02:06,436 --> 01:02:11,032
我尽量不想你
也不去想可能发生的事
I try not to think about you. About
what might be happening over there.

485
01:02:11,874 --> 01:02:14,035
但是,有时候躺在床上
But sometimes, when I'm lying in bed,

486
01:02:14,177 --> 01:02:17,476
忍不住担心你的处境
I can't keep myself
from wondering where you are.

487
01:02:17,613 --> 01:02:19,547
和过得好不好
How you're doing.

488
01:02:30,059 --> 01:02:32,027
你在干嘛?
What the hell you doin'?

489
01:02:32,695 --> 01:02:35,095
写信给我儿子
Writing a letter to my son.

490
01:02:35,231 --> 01:02:37,722
你忘了命令?不准流出一个字
Forget your orders? No letters out.

491
01:02:38,468 --> 01:02:41,596
上面不准邮件进入保育区
Command don't want postmarks
going to the reservation.

492
01:02:46,375 --> 01:02:48,206
没听到吗?
Hey! You hear me?

493
01:02:53,883 --> 01:02:57,182
我回家后他就看得到啦
I thought that he might read 'em
when I get home.

494
01:03:02,959 --> 01:03:04,984
他叫什么名字?
What's his name?

495
01:03:05,128 --> 01:03:06,993
你儿子
Your son.

496
01:03:07,430 --> 01:03:10,524
乔治,乔治华盛顿
It's George. George Washington.

497
01:03:12,001 --> 01:03:14,162
乔治华盛顿亚吉
George Washington Yahzee.

498
01:03:16,339 --> 01:03:18,466
听起来蛮响亮的
It's got a bit of a ring to it.

499
01:03:20,009 --> 01:03:21,909
我太太不太喜欢
My wife wasn't so sure.

500
01:03:22,445 --> 01:03:24,845
她比较传统
She's a little more traditional.

501
01:03:27,650 --> 01:03:30,118
-好漂亮的一家人
-给我看看,亚吉
- Nice-looking family.
- Let's see, Yahz.

502
01:03:30,253 --> 01:03:34,849
乔治很有个性
他有自己的想法
Yeah, that George, he's quite a character.
He's got a mind of his own.

503
01:03:38,427 --> 01:03:40,486
我可以抽一根吗?
Can I try one of those?

504
01:03:41,364 --> 01:03:44,197
-你抽烟?
-抽着玩的
- You smoke?
- Not really.

505
01:04:23,105 --> 01:04:25,505
-下来!
-快下车!
- Dismount!
- Get out of the truck!

506
01:04:26,676 --> 01:04:28,610
动作快!
Let's go! Let's go!

507
01:04:29,278 --> 01:04:31,178
-跟我来!
-走!
- Follow me!
- Let's go!

508
01:04:39,689 --> 01:04:41,554
我中弹了!
- I'm hit!
- Yahzee!

509
01:04:43,659 --> 01:04:45,217
亚吉
Yahzee!

510
01:04:46,762 --> 01:04:48,252
我中弹了!
I'm hit!

511
01:04:48,431 --> 01:04:50,592
拿下来!好烫!
Take it off! It burns!

512
01:04:55,137 --> 01:04:57,571
你没中弹,闭嘴!
You're not hit. Just shut up. You're not hit.

513
01:05:15,591 --> 01:05:17,957
-散开!
-动作快!
- Spread out!
- Move!

514
01:05:26,869 --> 01:05:29,497
-炸弹从哪来的?
-我们自己人
- Where the hell are they comin' from?
- From us.

515
01:05:29,605 --> 01:05:32,774
-什么?
-那不是日本人的炮
- What?
- They're not Jap guns.

516
01:05:33,976 --> 01:05:37,377
-自己人炸自己人?
-我们应该走四号路
- We're getting shot at by our own guys?
- We're supposed to be on road 04.

517
01:05:37,513 --> 01:05:39,310
-通知团部
-没办法!
- Get the regiment on the horn.
- I can't!

518
01:05:39,448 --> 01:05:43,782
-告诉他们炸到自己人
-不行!无线电炸坏了
- Tell 'em they're shelling...
- I can't! The radio's out. It's been hit.

519
01:05:46,789 --> 01:05:49,553
-他们炸太近了
-日本鬼子一定在我们前面
- They're firing too short!
- The Japs gotta be way ahead of us.

520
01:05:49,692 --> 01:05:51,216
想点办法
Do somethin'.

521
01:05:51,360 --> 01:05:53,760
跟我来
Shit... Follow me!

522
01:05:53,929 --> 01:05:56,591
-我们走错路了
-干!
- We're on the wrong fuckin' road!
- Goddamn it!

523
01:06:18,721 --> 01:06:20,188
完蛋了!
God.

524
01:06:42,945 --> 01:06:44,572
龟孙子
Son of a bitch!

525
01:07:06,435 --> 01:07:08,426
不要怕,老哥!
I got you, mac!

526
01:07:13,442 --> 01:07:15,205
救护兵!
Corpsman!

527
01:07:15,945 --> 01:07:18,675
救护兵!
Corpsman!

528
01:07:24,153 --> 01:07:26,144
救护兵!
Corpsman!

529
01:07:27,790 --> 01:07:29,690
奈里!
Nellie!

530
01:07:33,529 --> 01:07:35,429
救护兵!
Corpsman!

531
01:08:04,894 --> 01:08:07,089
你说的没错,乔伊
You were right, Joe.

532
01:08:07,897 --> 01:08:09,592
我长得像日本人
I do look like a Nip.

533
01:08:09,732 --> 01:08:11,757
你在说什么?
What the hell are you talking about?

534
01:08:11,901 --> 01:08:13,266
穿上他们的制服
Putting on that Jap uniform. 

535
01:08:13,402 --> 01:08:16,269
用他们的无线电
通知我方停火
Trying to get
one of their radios, call off our guns.

536
01:08:16,405 --> 01:08:19,101
-笨主意
-闭嘴,让他说完
- That's stupid.
- Shut up. Let him talk.

537
01:08:19,241 --> 01:08:22,301
-他不能出去
-这里不由你指挥,恩得斯
- He's not goin' out there.
- You're not in charge here, Enders.

538
01:08:22,445 --> 01:08:24,936
我身负命令,枪头
我要保护他
I got orders, Gunny.
He's my responsibility!

539
01:08:29,051 --> 01:08:32,350
他还年轻啊!
你们在杀自己人!
He's just a kid! You killed your own!

540
01:08:33,055 --> 01:08:37,685
你们有毛病啊!
你们在杀自己人!王八蛋!
What's wrong with you?
You killed your own! Sons of bitches!

541
01:08:38,527 --> 01:08:40,757
你们在杀自己人!
You killed your own!

542
01:08:56,412 --> 01:09:00,143
-你确定要这么做?
-马上就知道答案了,长官
- Sure you're up to this?
- Find out soon enough, sir.

543
01:09:03,085 --> 01:09:06,213
-你想干嘛?
-我跟他去
- What the hell are you doin' there?
- I'm goin' with him.

544
01:09:06,355 --> 01:09:08,550
如果你没意见的话
If that's OK with you.

545
01:09:12,027 --> 01:09:13,927
枪给我
Give me the rifle.

546
01:09:17,299 --> 01:09:19,494
Horyo-da.

547
01:09:20,135 --> 01:09:22,194
“战俘”的日本话
It's Jap for prisoner.

548
01:09:22,972 --> 01:09:24,963
Horyo-da.

549
01:09:32,982 --> 01:09:34,973
Horyo-da.

550
01:09:37,987 --> 01:09:40,251
好啦,大家准备
All right, everybody be ready.

551
01:10:38,047 --> 01:10:39,139
Horyo-da!

552
01:10:45,688 --> 01:10:46,814
冲啊!
Now!

553
01:10:58,934 --> 01:11:00,697
打我
Hit me. Hit me.

554
01:11:16,619 --> 01:11:18,553
不要打我!
Please don't hit me!

555
01:11:58,293 --> 01:11:59,590
亚吉
Yahzee!

556
01:12:09,038 --> 01:12:11,165
杀了他!
Kill him!

557
01:12:16,712 --> 01:12:18,805
快点,杀了他!
Goddamn it, kill him!

558
01:12:25,487 --> 01:12:27,250
去无线电那!
Get on the radio!

559
01:12:35,731 --> 01:12:38,757
白鲍威,这是红卡森!
Bowie White, Bowie White,
this is Carson Red!

560
01:12:41,403 --> 01:12:44,463
停火!你们在炸自己人!
Cease fire! Cease fire!
You're shelling marines!

561
01:12:45,908 --> 01:12:47,842
中士!
Sergeant!

562
01:12:50,379 --> 01:12:52,404
停火!
Cease fire! Cease fire!

563
01:12:55,584 --> 01:12:57,677
距离加325米,立刻射击!
Add 325, fire for effect!

564
01:12:58,987 --> 01:13:02,616
调整!加325米,立刻射击!
Redirect fire. Add 325, fire for effect.

565
01:13:03,258 --> 01:13:05,226
走啦!
Let's go!

566
01:13:07,629 --> 01:13:09,654
摇高点!快!
Crank it up! Let's go!

567
01:13:09,832 --> 01:13:11,424
开火!
Commence fire!

568
01:13:11,600 --> 01:13:13,363
开火!
Fire!

569
01:13:20,909 --> 01:13:22,433
奏效了
Well, I'll be.

570
01:13:49,304 --> 01:13:51,101
请问什么事,上校?
Colonel. Can I help you, sir?

571
01:13:51,240 --> 01:13:54,971
我想找一位恩得斯中士
约瑟夫恩得斯
I'm looking for Sergeant Enders.
Joseph F Enders.

572
01:13:56,178 --> 01:13:57,941
恩得斯
Enders.

573
01:14:06,555 --> 01:14:08,352
是的,长官
Yes, sir.

574
01:14:09,158 --> 01:14:12,355
据报你非常神勇
Report I read claims
you went above and beyond.

575
01:14:13,996 --> 01:14:15,122
长官
Sir?

576
01:14:15,264 --> 01:14:17,596
我们已推荐你接受表扬
You've been recommended
for commendation.

577
01:14:17,766 --> 01:14:20,963
我非常同意,但何必等待…
And I concur. But I don't see any point
in you having to wait around

578
01:14:21,103 --> 01:14:25,369
繁复的公文往返
for all those formalities
to work themselves out.

579
01:14:26,208 --> 01:14:28,574
我手边正好有个勋章
Not when I got one of these handy.

580
01:14:29,344 --> 01:14:31,744
恭喜,恩得斯
Congratulations, Enders.

581
01:14:31,880 --> 01:14:33,939
你救了不少同胞
You saved a lot of marines.

582
01:14:42,691 --> 01:14:47,355
这不是我一个人的功劳,长官
多亏了二等兵班亚吉的帮忙
I wasn't alone in that, sir. I couldn't have
done it without Private Ben Yahzee.

583
01:14:47,462 --> 01:14:52,733
对,那位印地安人
Oh... Right.
The, uh, Indian.

584
01:14:54,236 --> 01:14:57,763
抱歉,他是纳瓦荷人
母系苦水族
Begging the colonel's pardon,
he's a Navajo, of the Bitter Water People,

585
01:14:57,940 --> 01:14:59,874
父系塔楼族
born for the Towering House clan.

586
01:15:00,676 --> 01:15:06,171
当然,纳瓦荷人,塔楼族
Of course. Navajo. Towering House clan.

587
01:15:12,721 --> 01:15:14,882
继续保持下去,恩得斯
You keep up the good work, Enders.

588
01:15:53,629 --> 01:15:55,893
把这个寄给奈里的太太
Send that to Nellie's wife.

589
01:16:36,438 --> 01:16:39,236
每次都有你的信,恩得斯
You ever not miss mailcall, Enders?

590
01:16:46,214 --> 01:16:48,774
我妈说,人家花时间写信
My mom says somebody
takes the time to write a letter,

591
01:16:48,917 --> 01:16:51,078
你该花时间好好读
you should read the letter.

592
01:16:53,989 --> 01:16:56,423
你妈肯让你喝酒吗?
Does she let you drink, your mother?

593
01:16:57,092 --> 01:16:59,652
不肯,但她又不在这
No. But she's not here.

594
01:17:13,809 --> 01:17:17,506
-这是什么酒?
-确定不是法国红酒
- What is it?
- Well, it ain't Chianti, I'll tell you that.

595
01:17:17,646 --> 01:17:20,774
米酒类,是日本清酒
反正会醉就是了
It's rice wine. It's Jap sake.
But it does the trick.

596
01:17:24,353 --> 01:17:26,913
你有多少这种东西?
How much of this crap
do you have anyway?

597
01:17:29,758 --> 01:17:32,454
你这只耳朵有问题对不对?
You have a little trouble with that ear,
don't you, Joe?

598
01:17:32,561 --> 01:17:37,760
问题在内耳,耳鼓耳膜之类的
Ah, real problem's the inner ear.
It's anvils and stirrups and shit.

599
01:17:40,569 --> 01:17:42,662
我的平衡感不太好
I'm a little out of balance.

600
01:17:45,340 --> 01:17:48,366
你在山丘上表现很好,亚吉
You done good on that hill today, Yahzee.

601
01:17:48,577 --> 01:17:50,636
是啊,表现不错吧?
Yeah, I did, didn't I?

602
01:17:51,313 --> 01:17:53,975
一定了你一跳
I bet I surprised the shit out of you.

603
01:17:59,321 --> 01:18:01,653
你的情操很崇高,乔伊
It was a noble thing that you did, Joe.

604
01:18:02,357 --> 01:18:04,723
把银星勋章给奈里的太太
To give your Silver Star to Nellie's wife.

605
01:18:05,093 --> 01:18:07,220
我才不在乎奖章
I don't give a shit about medals.

606
01:18:17,506 --> 01:18:19,633
他们给我的第一枚
The first one they gave me...

607
01:18:21,309 --> 01:18:23,402
被我扔到海里去
I threw it into the ocean.

608
01:18:25,514 --> 01:18:27,982
那次是为了什么事?
What'd you get that one for?

609
01:18:28,116 --> 01:18:29,811
因为我撑着没死
For not dyin'.

610
01:18:31,620 --> 01:18:36,523
15个战友一起接受表扬
他们悉数阵亡
The 15 men who fought with me
got decorated too. For dying.

611
01:18:37,259 --> 01:18:38,783
所以…
So...

612
01:18:43,698 --> 01:18:46,758
中尉前一晚就战死了
Lieutenant was killed
the night before and...

613
01:18:48,637 --> 01:18:53,006
士官们也全死在登陆艇里
none of the sergeants even made it
out of the landing craft, so...

614
01:18:55,510 --> 01:18:58,638
所以只好由我指挥
我第一次发号施令
that left me in charge.
It was my first command.

615
01:19:00,882 --> 01:19:07,287
上面下令死守
某个鸟不拉屎的沼泽
Orders were to hold some shitty swamp
marsh on the ass-end of nowhere.

616
01:19:10,892 --> 01:19:12,826
我只好听命行事
And I did.

617
01:19:16,231 --> 01:19:19,166
我手下的弟兄
All of the men under my command...

618
01:19:24,606 --> 01:19:26,540
信任我的人
men who trusted me...

619
01:19:31,713 --> 01:19:35,114
全都求我撤退
who begged me to pull back...

620
01:19:39,821 --> 01:19:41,755
结果没有一个生还
not one of them made it.

621
01:19:45,694 --> 01:19:48,629
除了一个固执的浑球
Just one stupid asshole.

622
01:19:54,503 --> 01:19:57,870
他们因此给我银星勋章
And for that, they gave me the Silver Star.

623
01:20:00,976 --> 01:20:03,069
他们叫什么名字?
What were their names?

624
01:20:04,379 --> 01:20:06,904
说他们的故事
It might be good to tell a story about 'em.

625
01:20:07,582 --> 01:20:10,312
最好也知道他们的名字和长相
You know, who they were
and what they were like.

626
01:20:12,921 --> 01:20:18,052
纳瓦荷人鸟规矩真多
要干什么?
What a magical pile of Navajo horseshit.
What the hell for?

627
01:20:18,727 --> 01:20:20,786
向他们致敬
To honor them.

628
01:20:21,663 --> 01:20:23,563
纪念他们
Their memory.

629
01:20:24,666 --> 01:20:29,330
那不是你的错,乔伊
你是听命行事
You know, it wasn't your fault, Joe.
You were just followin' orders.

630
01:20:30,238 --> 01:20:31,967
是啊
Yeah.

631
01:20:32,107 --> 01:20:34,974
我是他妈的杰出陆战队
I'm a good fuckin' marine.

632
01:20:38,613 --> 01:20:40,979
所以派这个任务给我
That's why they gave me this detail.

633
01:20:45,654 --> 01:20:47,349
是喔
Yeah.

634
01:20:47,856 --> 01:20:50,120
我是他妈的杰出陆战队
I'm a good fuckin' marine.

635
01:21:19,955 --> 01:21:21,718
乔伊  怎么
- Joe!
- What?

636
01:21:27,128 --> 01:21:29,392
你他妈的,乔伊恩得斯
Goddamn you, Joe Enders!

637
01:21:29,564 --> 01:21:30,963
没错
Really.

638
01:21:47,716 --> 01:21:49,650
不要想太多
It's all right.

639
01:21:50,752 --> 01:21:53,186
来,乔伊,我扶你
Come on, Joe. I got you.

640
01:23:13,601 --> 01:23:15,501
干什么?
What the fuck?

641
01:23:20,642 --> 01:23:24,078
我没醉死,亚吉,别乱整
I ain't that drunk, Yahzee.
You cut that horseshit out.

642
01:23:53,408 --> 01:23:56,935
“塔那帕村第二侦查队”

643
01:23:58,380 --> 01:24:01,076
什么时候抵达村庄？
What's your expected arrival
to the village? Over.

644
01:24:01,883 --> 01:24:03,646
大约1500，空军侦查报告
Around 1500. Aerial Reconnaissance
reports

645
01:24:03,785 --> 01:24:05,309
没有活动，好像蛮安全的
 no movement, looks secure.

646
01:24:05,453 --> 01:24:07,614
要求热食与信件，完毕
Request hot chow and mailif possible.
Over.

647
01:24:09,324 --> 01:24:13,522
混合草莓与这瑞典玩意儿
就成了优酪乳
I'm gonna mix my daddy's strawberries in
this Swedish concoction called yoghurt.

648
01:24:13,628 --> 01:24:16,256
所幸美国人会自创口味
God willin', America
will develop the taste.

649
01:24:16,831 --> 01:24:21,393
战后你想干嘛,查理?
What about you, Charlie? What's life
got in store for you after this mess?

650
01:24:22,103 --> 01:24:25,769
奇克拿来当女朋友的绵羊?
Sheep? As in Chick's girlfriend, sheep?

651
01:24:27,509 --> 01:24:31,377
查理家的羊群是四州最多的
Charlie's family owns the biggest flock
in the Four Corners area.

652
01:24:31,513 --> 01:24:33,447
不是盖的?
No shit?

653
01:24:34,215 --> 01:24:37,514
-你是富翁嘛,白马
-还好啦
- You a rich man, Whitehorse?
- We do OK.

654
01:24:37,652 --> 01:24:41,986
我要成立计程车队
那是我致富的秘诀
Taxis. A whole stinkin' fleet of 'em.
That's how I'm making my millions.

655
01:24:43,124 --> 01:24:45,957
然后我要回到我的故乡
And then I'm goin' back
to the motherland.

656
01:24:46,060 --> 01:24:49,086
在圣多里尼峭壁盖栋别墅
I'm gonna build myself a villa
on the cliffs of Santorini.

657
01:24:49,264 --> 01:24:52,461
圣多里尼,哇,奢华
Ah, Santorini, my friends - that's living.

658
01:24:53,601 --> 01:24:56,764
不错,你呢,吉?
Sounds nice. What about you, Zee?

659
01:24:57,539 --> 01:24:59,370
我考虑去教书
Thinkin' about teaching.

660
01:24:59,507 --> 01:25:03,637
引进新知识到保育区
Ah, teaching. Bring a little something
back to the reservation?

661
01:25:03,778 --> 01:25:08,738
事实上,是将保育区的知识
介绍给全世界
Actually, more interested in bringing
some of the reservation back to the world.

662
01:25:08,883 --> 01:25:11,545
希望能到大学教美国历史
Hoping to teach college.
American history.

663
01:25:11,686 --> 01:25:13,551
很符合我们的需要
Oh, that's just what we need.

664
01:25:13,688 --> 01:25:18,489
亚吉告诉大学生
卡司特怎么在小彼弘被剥头皮
Yahzee teachin' college boys about
Custer's scalpin' at Little Bighorn.

665
01:25:19,227 --> 01:25:23,027
奇特卡森逼纳瓦荷人
迁徙三千哩又怎么说?
And what about Kit Carson, and what
they did to the Navajo in the Long Walk?

666
01:25:23,198 --> 01:25:25,598
没读过吧,奇克?
You ever read about that, Chick?

667
01:25:26,334 --> 01:25:28,234
一定没有
Didn't think so.

668
01:25:29,737 --> 01:25:31,637
你呢,乔伊?
How about you, Joe?

669
01:25:32,640 --> 01:25:35,336
-什么?
-战后你想干嘛?
- What?
- What are you doin' after this mess?

670
01:25:35,477 --> 01:25:37,411
战争总是会结束的
It's gotta end sometime.

671
01:25:41,149 --> 01:25:44,312
亲爱的乔伊,今天有个好消息
Dear Joe, we got great news today.

672
01:25:45,019 --> 01:25:49,080
罗斯福总统宣布取消
夏威夷的灯火管制
President Roosevelt announced
the end of blackouts on Hawaii.

673
01:25:49,224 --> 01:25:51,784
本以为遥遥无期
We thought the day would never come.

674
01:25:52,827 --> 01:25:56,957
10点仍有宵禁但影响不到我
There's still a ten o'clock curfew,
but it doesn't matter to me.

675
01:25:57,699 --> 01:26:02,363
值班12小时后
累得只有精力写信
After a 12-hour shift I'm too tired
to do anything but write letters.

676
01:26:05,139 --> 01:26:10,236
真正感觉到战况不错
战争随时都有可能结束了
There is a real sense that the war
is going well, and could be over soon.

677
01:26:12,747 --> 01:26:17,241
越来越想你
你到底是死是活呢?
I think about you more and more.
If you're alive or dead out there.

678
01:26:18,586 --> 01:26:22,716
我每天查信
心想迟早会有答案
I check the mailevery day, knowing
there's going to be an answer.

679
01:26:22,857 --> 01:26:25,189
你有收到我的信吗,乔伊?
Are you reading these, Joe?

680
01:26:25,727 --> 01:26:27,661
听到我的话吗?
Are you listening?

681
01:26:33,067 --> 01:26:35,763
-左翼没有危险
-这区没有危险
- We're secure on the left side.
- Area's secured.

682
01:26:35,904 --> 01:26:38,031
做好防御工事
Set up defense positions.

683
01:26:38,172 --> 01:26:40,333
奇克,负责扎营
Chick, bed 'em down for the night.

684
01:26:40,475 --> 01:26:42,204
哈利
Harri.

685
01:27:37,732 --> 01:27:39,063
怎么回事？
What's wrong?

686
01:27:40,068 --> 01:27:41,558
好痛
I'm hurting.

687
01:27:47,842 --> 01:27:50,174
这里有些止痛药
Here's some pain reliever.

688
01:28:03,691 --> 01:28:05,921
别担心，你没事
Don't worry, you'll be fine.

689
01:28:11,599 --> 01:28:12,793
谢谢，大叔
Thank you, Uncle.

690
01:28:32,654 --> 01:28:35,418
听起来蛮有感觉的
That's startin' to sound like something.

691
01:29:23,871 --> 01:29:25,998
不晓得你是个艺术家
I didn't know you were an artist.

692
01:29:26,441 --> 01:29:28,238
随便涂鸦
Oh, it's stupid.

693
01:29:28,376 --> 01:29:33,678
小时候常在祖母厨房桌上画
It's just something I would do as a kid
on my grandmother's kitchen table.

694
01:29:34,215 --> 01:29:36,115
很不错
Well, it's nice.

695
01:29:36,250 --> 01:29:38,184
你信天主教?
You Catholic?

696
01:29:40,755 --> 01:29:42,689
以前啦
I used to be.

697
01:29:44,258 --> 01:29:47,318
正好想起受坚信礼的事
I was thinkin' about
when they confirmed me.

698
01:29:47,462 --> 01:29:50,829
八岁那年,他们帮我抹圣水
I was eight, and they anointed me
with the holy water.

699
01:29:50,965 --> 01:29:53,058
我还记得
And I remember...

700
01:29:55,303 --> 01:29:57,828
他们说我是基督的战士
they told me I was a soldier of Christ.

701
01:30:01,676 --> 01:30:05,442
不晓得什么时候迷失了自己
I guess somewhere along the way
I must have switched units.

702
01:30:07,749 --> 01:30:09,683
是油
It's oil.

703
01:30:11,686 --> 01:30:14,951
坚信礼不用水,是用油
They don't use holy water to confirm.
They use oil.

704
01:30:15,923 --> 01:30:17,948
我家也信天主教
I was raised Catholic too.

705
01:30:18,626 --> 01:30:20,958
上保育区内的教会学校
Mission school on the reservation.

706
01:30:21,996 --> 01:30:26,194
神父作弥撒时
不喜欢我们说纳瓦荷语
It's funny. Fathers didn't like us
talking Navajo at Mass.

707
01:30:27,769 --> 01:30:30,169
有个礼拜天我忘记了
Of course, one Sunday I forgot.

708
01:30:31,672 --> 01:30:35,699
被处罚绑在地下室的暖炉上
They punished me by tying me
to the radiator in the basement.

709
01:30:35,843 --> 01:30:37,777
整整两天
For two days.

710
01:30:39,413 --> 01:30:41,074
记得我当时也是八岁
I think I was eight too.

711
01:30:42,049 --> 01:30:46,479
现在可以自由说纳瓦荷语了
Well, they're sure
lettin' you talk Navajo now.
Yeah.

712
01:30:53,394 --> 01:30:58,229
战争结束后
或许你该来看看纳瓦荷村
You know, when this is over, maybe
you should come out to Navajo country.

713
01:30:59,200 --> 01:31:02,931
纪念碑河谷很美,很幽静
Monument Valley is a beautiful place.
It's peaceful.

714
01:31:03,538 --> 01:31:06,837
可以尝试军队里没有的东西
You know, we could do some things
that you don't do in the Corps.

715
01:31:06,974 --> 01:31:12,469
比如骑马,吃炸面包,打猎
Like ride horses, eat fry bread,
do some hunting...

716
01:31:15,316 --> 01:31:17,250
骑马
Horses.

717
01:31:22,423 --> 01:31:25,859
再说啦
到亚历桑那有好长一段路
I don't know.
It's a pretty long drive to Arizona.

718
01:31:25,993 --> 01:31:29,656
很值得,你可以看看我儿子
But it might be worth it.
You know, you could meet my son.

719
01:31:30,331 --> 01:31:32,822
他也可以见见乔伊恩得斯
And he could meet Joe Enders,

720
01:31:33,768 --> 01:31:38,171
保护他瘦弱老爸的恩人
the guy who watched
over Daddy's scrawny ass.

721
01:31:42,810 --> 01:31:45,210
你一定是个好父亲,班
You must be a very good father, Ben.

722
01:31:47,081 --> 01:31:51,074
班?你以前不曾这样叫我
Ben. You know,
you've never called me that before.

723
01:31:53,087 --> 01:31:56,579
恩得斯是哪一国名字?
Enders. What kind of name
is that anyway?

724
01:31:57,291 --> 01:32:02,729
意大利,原本叫恩卓菲尼
被艾利斯岛移民局简化了
It's Italian. Used to be Endrolfini before
some asshole at Ellis Island got hold of it.

725
01:32:04,932 --> 01:32:08,163
上尉要发一封密码信到司令部
Captain needs to code a message
back to command post.

726
01:32:08,302 --> 01:32:09,792
你就是那个印地安人?
You the Indian?

727
01:32:09,937 --> 01:32:12,167
是的,我是那个印地安人
Yeah, I'm the Indian.

728
01:32:12,306 --> 01:32:15,639
只要几分钟,马上送你回来
It's just a few minutes' drive.
We'll get you back in no time.

729
01:32:41,369 --> 01:32:44,998
-我有话跟你说,枪头
-等我一下
- I need to speak with you, Gunny.
- Yeah. Give me a second.

730
01:32:45,539 --> 01:32:49,373
今天寄来的,吃过腌鲱鱼吗?
Got this with the mailtoday.
You ever had pickled herring?

731
01:32:51,746 --> 01:32:53,680
我想调职
I need out.

732
01:32:54,282 --> 01:32:56,773
你在说什么?
What the hell are you talkin' about?

733
01:32:56,918 --> 01:32:58,852
目前的职务
This detail.

734
01:32:59,320 --> 01:33:01,311
我的任务
My duty.

735
01:33:01,455 --> 01:33:03,389
我无法执行
I can't do it.

736
01:33:04,025 --> 01:33:06,186
我需要你,恩得斯
Well, I need you, Enders.

737
01:33:06,327 --> 01:33:08,989
你救过很多同胞的命
Yeah. You've been saving
a lot of marines.

738
01:33:12,900 --> 01:33:17,633
我要向营部司令申诉
我要调职
I'm requesting mast with
battalion commander. I want out.

739
01:33:19,140 --> 01:33:24,009
是吗?大家都是妈妈的儿子
谁不想调职
Oh, yeah? You and me and every
other mother's son. We all want out.

740
01:33:24,845 --> 01:33:28,542
只要东条英机和希特勒不死
Well, as long as there's
a Tojo and a Hitler out there

741
01:33:28,683 --> 01:33:31,709
我们就得继续战,懂吗?
we have to keep on fighting.
Is that understood?

742
01:33:33,287 --> 01:33:36,415
-你误会了
-我听得一清二楚
- You're not hearing me.
- I'm hearing you just fine.

743
01:33:37,325 --> 01:33:39,816
现在全世界都在打仗
Now, there's a war goin' on worldwide,

744
01:33:40,361 --> 01:33:43,728
没空理会你的需求和愿望
and it ain't bein' waged
on your wants and wishes.

745
01:33:43,864 --> 01:33:46,458
好好去睡一觉,这是命令
Now you get some sack time.
That's an order.

746
01:33:46,600 --> 01:33:48,795
去你的!我下不了手!
Goddamn it! I can't do it!

747
01:33:49,503 --> 01:33:51,733
我无法执行任务!
I can't perform my duty!

748
01:34:07,238 --> 01:34:09,263
嘿,小朋友
Hey there, sweetheart.

749
01:34:09,441 --> 01:34:11,432
嗨,没有关系
Hi. It's OK.

750
01:34:12,310 --> 01:34:15,245
不要哭,不会有事
You don't have to cry.
You're gonna be all right.

751
01:34:17,916 --> 01:34:19,975
我送一个礼物
Got a present for you.

752
01:34:22,487 --> 01:34:24,478
巧克力
This is chocolate.

753
01:34:26,324 --> 01:34:28,986
吃吃看,很好吃
You see, you eat it... and it's good.

754
01:34:33,865 --> 01:34:35,799
很好吃
It's good.

755
01:34:36,301 --> 01:34:38,428
要不要尝尝看?
You want some?

756
01:34:41,673 --> 01:34:43,607
下次记得先嚼一嚼
You'll have to chew it next time. Here.

757
01:34:55,286 --> 01:34:57,379
哈利根,走!
Harrigan, go!

758
01:35:08,033 --> 01:35:09,796
炸弹过来了!
Incoming!

759
01:35:18,610 --> 01:35:20,202
跑!
Run!

760
01:35:20,378 --> 01:35:21,777
走!快跑!
Go! Run!

761
01:35:21,946 --> 01:35:24,039
哈利根!叫她跑!
Harrigan! Make her run!

762
01:35:25,717 --> 01:35:27,651
快点!来这边!
Come on! To me!

763
01:35:45,437 --> 01:35:47,302
哈利根!
Harrigan!

764
01:36:54,172 --> 01:36:56,333
该走了!
Come on, keep moving!

765
01:37:20,231 --> 01:37:22,165
退回来!
Fall back!

766
01:38:25,129 --> 01:38:27,222
求救!求救!
Help! Help!

767
01:38:43,581 --> 01:38:45,549
不能让他们活捉我们
I can't let 'em take us.

768
01:38:48,653 --> 01:38:50,848
说什么呀?
What are you talking about?

769
01:39:42,340 --> 01:39:43,534
留他活口
Don't kill him.

770
01:39:43,775 --> 01:39:44,901
他很重要
He's important.

771
01:39:46,311 --> 01:39:48,211
我们需要拷问他
We need to interrogate him.

772
01:41:18,803 --> 01:41:20,737
恩得斯
Enders!

773
01:41:21,773 --> 01:41:23,968
我找不到公牛和白马
I can't find Ox or Whitehorse.

774
01:41:27,445 --> 01:41:29,310
你有看到他们吗?
Have you seen them?

775
01:41:30,715 --> 01:41:32,478
他在那里
He's over there.

776
01:41:36,087 --> 01:41:37,884
噢,天啊
Oh, shit...

777
01:41:57,175 --> 01:42:00,941
这里不是应该很安全吗?
怎么回事?
This was supposed to be a secured area!
What happened?

778
01:42:04,449 --> 01:42:06,781
我杀了他
I killed him.

779
01:42:07,752 --> 01:42:09,811
你什么?
You... you what?

780
01:42:10,555 --> 01:42:15,492
我用手榴弹
丢过去把他炸个粉碎
I took my grenade and...
and I threw it and I blew him up.

781
01:42:23,968 --> 01:42:26,232
你他妈的疯了!
What the hell is wrong with you?

782
01:42:28,506 --> 01:42:29,973
亚吉
Yahzee!

783
01:42:30,374 --> 01:42:33,376
亚吉,不要!
Yahzee! Yahzee, no!

784
01:42:33,478 --> 01:42:34,911
起来!
Get up!

785
01:42:39,951 --> 01:42:42,681
来呀,动手啊
Come on. You can do it.

786
01:42:42,820 --> 01:42:45,885
放过他
- Yahzee.
- Let him go.

787
01:42:46,023 --> 01:42:47,786
亚吉,不要
Yahzee, no.

788
01:42:49,060 --> 01:42:51,824
为何不…动手啊!
Go on. Why can't... Come on. Do it.

789
01:42:51,963 --> 01:42:53,897
-动手啊!
-不
- Do it!
- No.

790
01:43:26,797 --> 01:43:31,461
我们听说白马的事了，亚吉
我们会表扬他的功绩
We heard about Whitehorse, Yahzee. We
shall honor his name and his memory.

791
01:43:31,636 --> 01:43:33,570
再会，查理再会
Farewell, Charlie, farewell.

792
01:43:34,572 --> 01:43:37,871
是的，查理再会
Yes, Charlie, farewell.

793
01:43:51,222 --> 01:43:54,953
你知道,白马…救过我一命
You know, Whitehorse...
he saved my bacon.

794
01:43:58,930 --> 01:44:02,627
不知道乔治卡斯特会怎么想
Wonder what George Armstrong Custer
would make of that.

795
01:44:05,436 --> 01:44:10,669
记得祖父以前坐在廊下
讲猎印地安人的事
I remember my granddaddy sittin' on
the porch talkin' about huntin' Indians,

796
01:44:10,808 --> 01:44:13,902
讲得简直像猎地鼠一般
like he was talkin'
about gophers or somethin'.

797
01:44:15,313 --> 01:44:19,340
猎一个赚三块美金
About gettin' paid three dollars
per Comanche ear.

798
01:44:21,419 --> 01:44:23,944
我知道很难想像
I know. Gets you thinkin'.

799
01:44:25,823 --> 01:44:31,227
再过50年,或许我们
跟日本人会变成朋友
Another 50 years, who knows, we could
be sittin' down with the Nipponese.

800
01:44:31,362 --> 01:44:34,593
喝着清酒,随意哈拉
Drinkin' their sake, shootin' the shit...

801
01:44:36,867 --> 01:44:39,495
聊看看还可以打谁
lookin' for somebody else's ass to kick.

802
01:44:42,239 --> 01:44:44,139
你想太多了
You think too much.

803
01:44:49,347 --> 01:44:51,907
第一次有人这样称赞我
First time I ever been accused of that.

804
01:44:59,624 --> 01:45:02,991
“海陆第八营第二侦察连
塞班岛”

805
01:45:54,578 --> 01:45:58,309
告诉过你别一个人到处晃
Thought I told you not to go
traipsing around on your own.

806
01:46:05,189 --> 01:46:10,525
你知道,查理祝福过我儿子
出生时,以纳瓦荷传统方式
You know, Charlie blessed my son
in the Navajo way the day he was born.

807
01:46:17,601 --> 01:46:20,900
他曾怀疑老美会保护我们
He wondered about cowboys
watching Indians' backs.

808
01:46:21,639 --> 01:46:24,005
老是感觉不对劲
Something about it didn't seem right.

809
01:46:24,775 --> 01:46:27,642
我觉得查理只是多心
I thought it was Charlie just being Charlie.

810
01:46:29,046 --> 01:46:34,143
他其实一点都不想来打仗
是我说服他的
He didn't even want to come
to this damn war. I talked him into it.

811
01:46:38,355 --> 01:46:40,084
或许你错了
Maybe you made a mistake.

812
01:46:51,635 --> 01:46:53,830
大家可能都错了
Maybe we all did.

813
01:46:55,072 --> 01:46:56,937
我只是奉命行事,班
I was following orders, Ben.

814
01:46:58,275 --> 01:47:00,937
我奉命保护密码
My orders were to protect the code.

815
01:47:01,812 --> 01:47:07,375
如果你们其中一人被补
一旦密,密码就没用了
If one of you got caught, talked,
the code would be useless.

816
01:47:14,959 --> 01:47:16,984
我只是奉命行事,班
I was following orders, Ben.

817
01:47:20,164 --> 01:47:24,624
当然是,乔伊
你是他妈的杰出军人
Course you were, Joe.
You're a damn good fuckin' marine.

818
01:47:40,184 --> 01:47:42,209
海盗要找你
The Viking wants to see you.

819
01:47:43,220 --> 01:47:45,245
他说马上
He says right away.

820
01:47:52,530 --> 01:47:55,522
跟大伙说明一下怎么回事
I want you to brief everybody,
make clear what's happenin'.

821
01:47:55,699 --> 01:47:58,361
我打头阵没问题,枪头
All right. Got no problem
with point, Gunny.

822
01:47:58,435 --> 01:47:58,696
我打头阵没问题,枪头
All right. Got no problem
with point, Gunny.

823
01:48:00,671 --> 01:48:01,865
Yeah.

824
01:48:02,006 --> 01:48:06,136
第八营已经出发了
我们要迎头赶上,领先他们
The 8th is moving out already
and we need to be ahead of 'em.

825
01:48:06,243 --> 01:48:10,043
目标是那边那块巨石
The destination is that big piece of rock
you see over there.

826
01:48:10,181 --> 01:48:13,514
这个岛的最后防御据点
The last defensible ridge on this island.

827
01:48:13,651 --> 01:48:18,281
攻下那山头
塞班几乎就是我们的了
Now, thinkin' is, we take the mount,
Saipan is pretty much ours.

828
01:48:22,092 --> 01:48:26,153
昨天轰炸机
把山头炸得差不多了
Yesterday, bombers
beat the shit out of that rock.

829
01:48:26,564 --> 01:48:30,796
上面很紧张,可能遭到顽抗
The brass is nervous. They expected
more resistance over there.

830
01:48:31,802 --> 01:48:34,327
要我们过去查看一下
Now they want us to go over
and check it out.

831
01:48:35,472 --> 01:48:37,997
他们要我们去哪里?
So where the hell they got us now?

832
01:48:38,142 --> 01:48:40,007
翻上山头
Goin' up the mountain.

833
01:48:40,477 --> 01:48:42,741
偷窥一下
Have ourselves a little peek.

834
01:48:44,949 --> 01:48:48,612
要密码战士打头阵是有原因的
That codetalker is out front for a reason.

835
01:48:49,153 --> 01:48:51,587
他正好派上用场
That's exactly where I need him to be.

836
01:48:52,790 --> 01:48:55,486
假如你俩之间有嫌隙
If there's still a problem
between the two of you,

837
01:48:55,626 --> 01:48:59,221
最好现在立刻摆平
I would like to straighten that out,
right here, right now.

838
01:49:01,332 --> 01:49:03,892
-我没事的,枪头
-好极了
- No problem here, Gunny.
- That's good.

839
01:49:04,735 --> 01:49:06,828
但我还有一个问题
But there's still one here.

840
01:49:08,405 --> 01:49:11,067
你只须做你该做的事
You just do what you're
supposed to do, Sergeant.

841
01:49:11,208 --> 01:49:13,233
不多也不少
Nothing more, nothing less.

842
01:49:19,516 --> 01:49:21,450
恩得斯
Enders.

843
01:49:22,653 --> 01:49:24,814
恩得斯,又一封你的信
You got another letter.

844
01:50:30,187 --> 01:50:32,018
不要动!
Freeze!

845
01:50:43,133 --> 01:50:46,967
要命!我们站在地雷区中央!
Jesus Christ! We're in the middle
of a goddamn minefield!

846
01:50:47,104 --> 01:50:49,629
奇克会带我们脱离的,是吧?
Chick's gonna get us out. Right, Chick?

847
01:50:50,474 --> 01:50:52,408
当然
Sure I am.

848
01:50:54,111 --> 01:50:56,204
跟着奇克排一纵队
One line after Chick.

849
01:51:01,085 --> 01:51:03,019
帕帕斯
Pappas.

850
01:51:05,155 --> 01:51:06,952
帕帕斯
Pappas.

851
01:51:08,158 --> 01:51:10,092
走呀,希腊人
Move, Greek.

852
01:51:10,694 --> 01:51:13,356
我的蛋蛋会被炸个粉碎!
I'm gonna get my fuckin' balls
blown off out here!

853
01:51:20,838 --> 01:51:22,772
亚吉,站住!
Yahzee! Stop!

854
01:51:44,862 --> 01:51:46,796
躲开!
Move out!

855
01:52:26,537 --> 01:52:27,970
亚吉
Yahzee!

856
01:52:46,223 --> 01:52:48,282
射得好,帕帕斯
Nice shootin', Pap.

857
01:53:07,611 --> 01:53:11,240
第八营进来了,查看另一边
The 8th's movin' in.
We'd better check out the other side.

858
01:53:11,381 --> 01:53:13,406
了解,你还好吧?
Got it. You all right?

859
01:53:14,284 --> 01:53:18,050
奇克负责左翼,恩得斯到右翼
我们会用榴弹炮掩护你们
Chick, take the left flank. Enders, go right.
We'll cover you with a 30.

860
01:53:18,188 --> 01:53:19,849
